  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You awaken in Anomalum, trapped in an endless nightmare. Carefully observe your surroundings and check the clock to escape. In this psychological horror game, attention to detail and exploration of liminal spaces are crucial to freeing yourself from the nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/f05611a22f79173617ed2222bf9483db.poster.avif?t=1761183105\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/f05611a22f79173617ed2222bf9483db.webm?t=1761183105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/f05611a22f79173617ed2222bf9483db.mp4?t=1761183105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RULES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not ignore any anomalies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you detect anomalies, retreat immediately. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If there are no anomalies, advance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The time on the clocks will indicate if you are making progress.[/b]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/5257b68d9f40f7c81660ef35c0ff0ab6.poster.avif?t=1761183105\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/5257b68d9f40f7c81660ef35c0ff0ab6.webm?t=1761183105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/5257b68d9f40f7c81660ef35c0ff0ab6.mp4?t=1761183105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventure and exploration[/b] inspired by TheExit8, with new places to discover. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging puzzles[/b] that require analysis of the environment for anomalies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive atmosphere[/b] with enveloping sounds and detailed graphics that immerse you in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PLAYTIME</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20~30 mins</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Anomalum</i> challenges you to use your perception to find the way out. Can you escape?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You awaken in Anomalum, trapped in an endless nightmare. Carefully observe your surroundings and check the clock to escape. In this psychological horror game, attention to detail and exploration of liminal spaces are crucial to freeing yourself from the nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/f05611a22f79173617ed2222bf9483db.poster.avif?t=1761183105\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/f05611a22f79173617ed2222bf9483db.webm?t=1761183105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/f05611a22f79173617ed2222bf9483db.mp4?t=1761183105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RULES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not ignore any anomalies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you detect anomalies, retreat immediately. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If there are no anomalies, advance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The time on the clocks will indicate if you are making progress.[/b]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/5257b68d9f40f7c81660ef35c0ff0ab6.poster.avif?t=1761183105\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/5257b68d9f40f7c81660ef35c0ff0ab6.webm?t=1761183105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050480/extras/5257b68d9f40f7c81660ef35c0ff0ab6.mp4?t=1761183105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventure and exploration[/b] inspired by TheExit8, with new places to discover. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging puzzles[/b] that require analysis of the environment for anomalies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive atmosphere[/b] with enveloping sounds and detailed graphics that immerse you in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PLAYTIME</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20~30 mins</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Anomalum</i> challenges you to use your perception to find the way out. Can you escape?</p>",
